text: Sándor Bognár (born 15 November 1950) is a Hungarian equestrian. He competed in the team jumping event at the 1972 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1950 births Category:Living people Category:Hungarian male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Hungary Category:Equestrians at the 1972 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Budapest
